<% provide(:title, 'Help') %>


<div class="container-fluid">
<div class="row-fluid">
    <h1>Help Page</h1>
    <h2>Welcome to RedRock Capital</h2>

    <p>Hello Customers, here are the actions you can do on each page:
    </p>
<h3>HomePage</h3>

      <ul>
        <li> View a customers current stock holdings</li>
        <li> personalize stock suggestions based on stock type</li>
        <li> send request to employee to order a stock</li>
      </ul>



<h3>Order Page</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>History of all current and past orders a customer has placed</li>
    <li>send request to order a stock</li>
    <li>Create conditional orders (hidden-stop and trailing-stop)</li>

  </ul>


<h3>Search Page (for stocks)</h3>

  <p>In our search page you can search for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>stocks available of a particular type</li>
    <li>stocks available with a particular keyword or set of keywords </li>
    <li>Best seller list of stocks</li>
  </ul>



<h3>Individual stock page</h3>

  <ul>
    <li>Show share price history for a given stock</li>
    <li>Show the most recent orders of the stock</li>
  </ul>



  <h1>Employee</h1>
<p> Below are our functions for employees on each page
</p>

  <h3>Homepage</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Record an order</li>
    <li>Produce a customer mailing list</li>
    <li>Approve or disapprove an order</li>
    <li>Produce a list of stock suggestions for a given client</li>
    <li>View Past/pending orders</li>
  </ul>


  <h1>Managers (Employee)</h1>
  <p> Below are our functions for Managers on each page
  </p>

  <h3>Homepage</h3>
  <ul>
      <li>Obtain a sales report for a month</li>
    <li>Produce a list of all stocks</li>
    <li>Produce a summary listing of revenue generated by a particular stock or by customer</li>
    <li>Determine which employee generated the most total revenue</li>

  </ul>

  <h3>Market Page</h3>
  <ul>

    <li>Produce a comprehensive listing of stocks</li>
    <li>set the share price of a stock</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Orders Page</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Produce a list of orders by a stock symbol or a customer name</li>
    <li>Produce a list of most actively traded stocks</li>
  </ul>
</div>
</div>
